ium/arab-states-implore-senior-eu-officials-to-recognize-a-palestinian-state/0000018f-be1b-df6b-a3ff-fe3b5e0a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击拉法后，致命大火在加沙人中蔓延绝望和悲伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/deadly-fire-spreads-despair-grief-among-gazans-after-israeli-strike/0000018f-be05-d475-a5cf-feffa1ee0000</link><description>加沙卫生当局称，有 45 人死亡，其中大部分是妇女、儿童和老人。一名难民营居民说：“在巴勒斯坦，我们的孩子、长辈、妇女和家园每天都在燃烧”</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 07:37:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/deadly-fire-spreads-despair-grief-among-gazans-after-israeli-strike/0000018f-be05-d475-a5cf-feffa1ee0000</guid></item><item><title>个性化噬菌体疗法治愈了从三层楼摔下来的耶路撒冷猫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-05-28/ty-article-magazine/cat-in-jerusalem-who-fell-three-stories-healed-with-personalized-bacteriophage-therapy/0000018f-ba3e-dca9-a5cf-be3ee4360000</link><description>暹罗猫“吱吱”折断了两条后腿，一条腿被截肢，另一条腿的植入物遭受慢性感染。进入高科技医学领域，进行人体测试</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 06:28:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-05-28/ty-article-magazine/cat-in-jerusalem-who-fell-three-stories-healed-with-personalized-bacteriophage-therapy/0000018f-ba3e-dca9-a5cf-be3ee4360000</guid></item><item><title>资料来源：以色列国防军内部报告发现两名加沙人在前往以色列监狱的途中被殴打死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/sources-idf-report-finds-two-gazans-died-after-being-beaten-en-route-to-israeli-prison/0000018f-bbbb-df3d-abbf-bffb68980000</link><description>两名被拘留者正从加沙地带被带到 Sde Teiman 拘留所；几名士兵受到谨慎审问，但没有人因涉嫌造成死亡而被捕</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 05:26:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/sources-idf-report-finds-two-gazans-died-after-being-beaten-en-route-to-israeli-prison/0000018f-bbbb-df3d-abbf-bffb68980000</guid></item><item><title>寻求庇护者在特拉维夫厄立特里亚政权支持者和反对者之间的斗殴中丧生</title><link>https:/