-cease-fire-even-without-a-hostage-deal/0000018f-bba5-d5c5-a3ff-fbad95c50000</link><description>以色列国防军正在向城市推进，但即使是强制撤离也没有解决密集地区的作战问题，看来部队的压力是行动的主要困难</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 20:23:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/civilian-deaths-in-rafah-could-force-israel-into-a-cease-fire-even-without-a-hostage-deal/0000018f-bba5-d5c5-a3ff-fbad95c50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列新征兵部队被派往加沙贾巴利亚，只受过最低限度的训练</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-new-israeli-army-conscripts-sent-to-gazas-jabalya-with-minimal-training/0000018f-bb40-dc1f-abef-ff79e0270000</link><description>“他们到达时有点震惊，但几天后，爆炸就成了家常便饭”：当新武装的以色列国防军新兵通常仍在训练时，他们现在发现自己身处加沙战场的中心</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 20:07:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-new-israeli-army-conscripts-sent-to-gazas-jabalya-with-minimal-training/0000018f-bb40-dc1f-abef-ff79e0270000</guid></item><item><title>欧洲外交官警告拉法罢工将加大对以色列接受停火的压力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/european-diplomats-warn-rafah-strike-could-lead-to-strict-interpretation-of-icj-orders/0000018f-bb65-d5c5-a3ff-fb6dd0720000</link><description>尽管国际法院上周限制以色列在拉法行动的命令“足够模糊，足以让各国能够视而不见”，但欧洲外交官警告说，以色列从夜间到周一对拉法的致命袭击可能会改变局面</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 19:35:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/european-diplomats-warn-rafah-strike-could-lead-to-strict-interpretation-of-icj-orders/0000018f-bb65-d5c5-a3ff-fb6dd0720000</guid></item><item><title>庆祝拉法巴勒斯坦人死亡的右翼分子是以色列的“真面目”吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-27/ty-article/.highlight/are-right-wingers-celebrating-palestinian-deaths-in-rafah-the-true-face-of-israel/0000018f-baee-dfb0-a7af-fbfe52ac0000</link><description>有人说，这才是以色列真正的丑恶嘴脸。那些相信并且了解一个不同的以色列的人面临着证明事实并非如此的不可能的挑战</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 19:20:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-27/ty-article/.highlight/are-right-wingers-celebrating-palestinian-deaths-in-rafah-the-true-face-of-israel/0000018f-baee-dfb0-a7af-fbfe52ac0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列电视曝光揭露内塔尼亚胡主要部长涉嫌严重腐败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-tv-expose-uncovers-alleged-deep-corruption-of-key-netanyahu-minister/0000018f-bab5-d0b7-abdf-feb7c40f0000</link><description>以色列警察和总检察长等众多观众热切观看了交通部长米里·雷格夫的两集电视特别节目，并宣布他们正在调查她在任期间的行为</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 17:47:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-tv-expose-uncovers-alleged-deep-corruption-of-key-netanyahu-minister/0000018f-bab5-d0b7-abdf-feb7c40f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼部长本-格维尔传唤警察局长进行谴责，尽管他无权这样做</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/israeli-minister-ben-gvir-summons-top-cop-for-reprimand-despite-lacking-authority-to-do-so/0000018f-baf5-d19e-a19f-fef734af0000</link><description>以色列国家安全部长在给该专员的一封信中声称，“最近对你总体功能失调的指控越来越多”，并补充说，“你唯一做得好的事情就是提拔与你关系密切的官员”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 17:22:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/israeli-minister-ben-gvir-summons-top-cop-for-reprimand-despite-lacking-authority-to-do-so/0000018f-baf5-d19e-a19f-fef734af0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 234 天：哈马斯称因拉法死亡将不会参加停战谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-234-hamas-says-it-wont-attend-truce-talks-because-of-rafah-deaths/0000018f-bae3-d5c5-a3ff-fbeb99740001</link><description>以色列国防军证实，拉法针对哈马斯高级成员的袭击导致附近帐篷营地起火，造成 45 名平民死亡 ■ 埃及士兵在拉法过境点与以色列军队发生冲突时丧生 ■ 卡塔尔外交部：以色列对拉法的袭击可能会阻碍停战谈判 ■ 哈马斯消息来源称由于拉法的死亡而不会参加谈判 ■ 战争进入 234 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 16:37:14 GMT</