a3ff-be3d898a0000</guid></item><item><title>这是以色列面临的最大威胁。这不是哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-is-the-greatest-threat-facing-israel-its-not-hamas/0000018f-b929-d24f-a5df-ffef4c4f0000</link><description>以色列正在进行第二次独立战争，同时面临生存威胁。但这种威胁来自我们内部</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 14:07:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-is-the-greatest-threat-facing-israel-its-not-hamas/0000018f-b929-d24f-a5df-ffef4c4f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>